snippet.textDisplay:
GOOSEBUMPS . GOOSEBUMPS. GOOSEBUMPS ALL AROUND.
After such a long time, I listened  something which gave me sheer happiness and bliss out of this world. 
Mame Khan is a legend. Salute to him. The expressions in his voice is hard to express in words. 
No words to explain how exemplary Amit Trivedi is !
And the best part was, how happy every instrumentalist was, enjoying the moment , syncing in with each other. Thank you each and every one for being so amazing ! Lots of love.
